cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SD, cs.MM

This paper deals with the problem of cross-modal domain transfer using deep generative models. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves unsupervised translation and alignment of attributes, which could fall under cs.SD (Sound) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
